{"tid":1804871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個小小嘅wiz*one,我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-12-31T10:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T10:33:23.000Z","uid":213300,"like":6,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"78c82b8124e2dcc4411b841f4c5a48528e9f5e40","tid":1804871,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n我係冇睇過pd48而直接飯iz*one<br />\n當初係畀佢哋12個<br />\n靚女有活力又可愛而吸引到<br />\n本命牙周同真真<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坦白講乜嘢做假<br />\n我唔知 我唔識 我唔清楚<br />\n就算係錯嘅<br />\n都唔係佢哋12個細路女錯啦<br />\n根本佢哋都係受害者<br />\n無啦啦要中止活動仲畀人話做假<br />\n真係戥佢哋可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界係有好彩唔好彩㗎喇<br />\n其他輸咗嗰啲咪當佢地今次唔好彩囉<br />\n最緊要下次有得好彩返㗎嘛<br />\n好心啲盲反嘅黑粉<br />\n咪大造文章造分化啦<br />\n好嘔心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重要嘅係<br />\n我哋wiz*one亦都只會認呢12個係唯一嘅iz*one<br />\n12個成員缺一不可<br />\n唔理佢乜柒做票做假喇<br />\n我想講嘅嘢就係咁多<br />\n最後祝iz*one快啲CB<br />\nCB大發<br />\n最好就永續iz*one啦<br />\n一位小小嘅wiz*one上"},{"pid":"e4e2805b38b51b3408c2c167456d41c75cb39d82","tid":1804871,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"樓煮说嘚豪岩。⋯⋯😢"},{"pid":"f537ce16f668a11e086f90394e7851c0facb1592","tid":1804871,"uid":48577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"死啦 樓主又黑IZ*ONE"},{"pid":"fad5f017e2d79260c945cda72e79de562ec31017","tid":1804871,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4e2805b38b51b3408c2c167456d41c75cb39d82","tid":1804871,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"樓煮说嘚豪岩。⋯⋯😢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T10:06:34.000Z","msg":"G持永續iz*one<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" c